public class AcademicStaff
extends RegisteredUser

The AcademicStaff class represents records of staffs.

The AcademicStaff class is subclass of RegisteredUserr, which makes it also implements Serializable interface.

title - Initial title

isCoordinator - A boolean that represents whether staff is a coordinator

getStatus

public boolean getStatus()
Return a boolean representing whether staff is activated. An AcademicStaff object is activated when it is created first time. It will be set as not activated when staff is deleted, and will be set as activated again if the same staff come back to department and is going to register again.

Returns:
True if staff is activated. Otherwise, return false.
